post.description:
Retrieve daily SPL token balances for multiple account addresses in a time-series format.
This endpoint aggregates native SOL, staked SOL, and SPL token holdings, and presents a combined portfolio value in USDoffering a comprehensive overview of all specified accounts.
The tokens included reflect the default filters of the token-balances endpoint: a trade minimum of 100, a trade volume minimum of 100,000 USD, and a holder minimum of 50.

days.description:
Number of previous days to include in the data (from today's date).
Allowed values range from 1 to 30, default to 2 weeks (14 days)

vybeTokenFilter.description: Whether Vybe's token filter should restrict the tokens that are returned. If false, all priced tokens are included. Default is true.

wallets.description: Wallets to include in the returned results (max 10).

blockTime.description: The timestamp, rounded to the day, of which this account snapshot was taken

stakeValue.description: The value of staked SOL in USD

stakeValueSol.description: The value of staked SOL in SOL

systemValue.description: The value of held System SOL in USD

tokenValue.description: Combined value of valid SPL tokens in USD.

get.description:
Retrieves a list of tracked tokens.

Allows sorting based on token fields: mintAddress, currentSupply, marketCap, name, price and symbol.

Useful for overview of past 24 hours' activity of listed tokens.

Results are paginated via page query parameter.

parameters.description: Optional ascending sort field specification. Only one of sort_by_asc or sort_by_desc can be used
parameters.name: sortByAsc

parameters.description: Optional descending sort field specification. Only one of sort_by_asc or sort_by_desc can be used
parameters.name: sortByDesc

parameters.description: Result page size specifier.
parameters.name: limit

parameters.description: Page selection, 0-indexed.
parameters.name: page

mintAddress.description: The public key of the token of interest

price.description: Current price in USD

price1d.description: Price in USD of the token 1 day ago

price7d.description: Price in USD of the token 7 days ago

tokenAmountVolume24h.description: Token volume transferred in past 24 hours

updateTime.description: Time of last update of price

usdValueVolume24h.description: Token volume transferred in past 24 hours USD value
